    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>这是一个有谜题元素的2D动作游戏。<br></li><li>玩家可以操作时间。利用这种能力来对付陷阱和敌人。<br></li><li>在限定时间内朝着任意关卡中的终点前进吧。<br></li><li>通过收集道具，玩家可以解锁更多能力。<br></li><li>可以创建并玩自己设计的关卡。</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >时间操作</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>倒带：时间倒流。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/b4948772e264336ebedc21e07cf73d98.poster.avif?t=1694243017\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/b4948772e264336ebedc21e07cf73d98.webm?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/b4948772e264336ebedc21e07cf73d98.mp4?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>减速：时间变慢。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/1d9d5e9fbbb7d11159b1f9df003e2541.poster.avif?t=1694243017\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/1d9d5e9fbbb7d11159b1f9df003e2541.webm?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/1d9d5e9fbbb7d11159b1f9df003e2541.mp4?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>停止：时间停止，此时玩家无敌。但使用完能力后，需要等待一段时间才能再次使用。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/2ebf44562ade0d3d5332e9a2d6ced6d8.poster.avif?t=1694243017\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/2ebf44562ade0d3d5332e9a2d6ced6d8.webm?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/2ebf44562ade0d3d5332e9a2d6ced6d8.mp4?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >编辑器</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过放置方块、敌人和陷阱，可以创建自己的关卡。<br></li><li>创建的关卡可以通过网络上传。<br></li><li>可以下载其他玩家设计的关卡并进行游戏。</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/0bbf828a7a04d59d9cd529ba2ed6d0f5.poster.avif?t=1694243017\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/0bbf828a7a04d59d9cd529ba2ed6d0f5.webm?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2335480/extras/0bbf828a7a04d59d9cd529ba2ed6d0f5.mp4?t=1694243017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2></h2>",
